{"tid":986588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA推算土星環最多僅1億歲　學者：非常年輕","createTime":"2019-01-18T15:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T15:29:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"900d8833b0d1a24da271f48b76aaa8ec05f502d5","tid":986588,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190118/s00005/c4662d4c0380e3fc9960b2c0b0b3c87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2Fc4662d4c0380e3fc9960b2c0b0b3c87b.jpg&h=54ddc6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（NASA圖片/明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n圍繞土星的土星環如何形成及何時形成，一直是未解謎團。多國科學家利用美國太空總署（NASA）的土星探測船「卡西尼」號（Cassini）搜集的數據，計算出土星環形成時期介乎1000萬至1億年前，跟恐龍在地球上生活的時期差不多，其總質量則只是過往估計的1/20。<br />\n<br />\n卡西尼號在2017年傳送最後一批數據後，已墜落土星大氣層自毀。它在最後任務階段曾6度穿過土星環的最內圈，藉此確定星體引力場和土星環質量。意大利羅馬大學教授耶斯（Luciano Iess）聯同美國及以色列的學者，利用卡西尼號的數據，研究土星環質量與形成時期。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，土星環質量有1.54億億公噸（1.54 x 1019 千克），只有過去學者推斷的1/20，約是其衛星土衛一的四成。他們又從探測器收集的土星環星塵比例數據，計算出土星環約在1000萬至1億年前形成；跟6500萬年前活躍於地球的恐龍生活時期相若。<br />\n<br />\n科學家傾向相信，土星在45億年前跟太陽系其他星球一同形成，因此相對於整個太陽系的年齡，土星環的形成，就像是「昨日」才發生的事情。耶斯團隊的研究在周四（17日）刊登於《科學》期刊。<br />\n<br />\n早有說法指，土星環既非於星球形成之初就存在，亦不會永遠圍繞土星。上月另有研究指出，土星環受到土星的引力影響，環上物質正持續墜落其大氣層，每小時有相當於2個奧運標準泳池的物質流失。科學家估計，整個土星環或會約在1億年內消失。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC/Science Daily）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190118/s00005/1547806331350/nasa%E6%8E%A8%E7%AE%97%E5%9C%9F%E6%98%9F%E7%92%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%83%851%E5%84%84%E6%AD%B2-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2F1547806331350%2Fnasa%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2583%25851%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595&d=asQxQC2wHI%2FrIUCZzsO9mGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=9ebd21e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00005%2F1547806331350%2Fnasa%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2583%25851%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595&h=7472796e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190118/s00005/1547806331350/nasa%E6%8E%A8%E7%AE%97%E5%9C%9F%E6%98%9F%E7%92%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%83%851%E5%84%84%E6%AD%B2-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95</a>"},{"pid":"d49531d01c59b24040948ee9854ba0e4ad66ddf0","tid":986588,"uid":93649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"土星環好靚好特別"},{"pid":"f8a12e64be2306f61c543ad7848b2eba7e14626b","tid":986588,"uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"1000萬都1億歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如作到100萬到10億歲啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7d9522c8621ab2acab96a229362b5ab67aa952","tid":986588,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a12e64be2306f61c543ad7848b2eba7e14626b","tid":986588,"uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"1000萬都1億歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如作到100萬到10億歲啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"1000萬都1億歲 有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20